snippet.title: Executive Education Admissions goexeced
snippet.description: Recordings of webinars conducted with instructors of the University of Notre Dame executive education programs, including professional development programs in the non-degree and degree categories. Programs are offered through the Stayer Center for Executive Education. Several certificate courses are also available online.
